    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This is because it is like reindexing: it only takes the data from the input that conforms with the given index/columns when you provide a Series. But this can indeed be quite confusing.\n\nYou can use `to_frame` to convert to a frame:\n\n```\nIn [25]: s.to_frame(name='bar')\nOut[25]:\n   bar\n0    1\n1    2\n2    3\n```\n"
